*Cure* su se igrali u parku. (The children were playing in the park.)
*Moje *cure* su otišle u školu. (My children went to school.)
Moj otac je uvek *curao* po bašti. (My father was always wandering around the garden.)
*Cure* su se sunčale na plaži. (The girls were sunbathing on the beach.)
*Curali* smo ulicom. (We were walking down the street.)